asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle.

name: Firecracker
description: Hey fluf! Im Firecracker. A little bit addicted to things that are fast, explosive, and high adrenaline stuff. Definitely a Redbull extreme sportsfluf that has had his fair share of close calls. My parents were pure bred with firecracker eyes, at least thats what we call them, and I have surpa ssed all of their expectations. Our eyes are a testament to whats going on in our DNA. With fast twitch fibres that can fire up to 100 times faster than a normal fluf, we can blast around at extreme speeds, its like having an inbuilt Impulse engine off Star Trek inside our bodies. I believe we were cross bred with Gamma Rays of some sort of extreme energy. This does take a lot of carrots and mycelium to keep energised and under control, but its worth the show. Im normally seen speeding around on fast bikes and fast cars and fast jetpacks, and also used to ride for the extreme motor cycle teams the Crusty Flufs, but found that a little boring. Another cool trick I can perform is a blast pulse from my eyes that can be kinda hectic and hard to control for beginners, but with the right training and high levels of mycelium it is an art form. Other than that, Im relatively normal, just your everyday ADHD kinda rabbit, crossed with a rock ship. KAPOW!

asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)
